{"tid":1889980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"非洲學生為中国打氣","createTime":"2020-02-21T02:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T03:04:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c261beb63bc7310b48b8457d334820d1f210f62b","tid":1889980,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T02:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20200221/s00053/e6ea724fa21e91598b8f053bc470e4d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20200221%2Fs00053%2Fe6ea724fa21e91598b8f053bc470e4d0.jpg&h=bc93ddb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】中國新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情已傳播至20多個國家，引起全球關注。2月19日，在肯尼亞首都內羅畢，馬薩雷貧民窟的小學生展示寫着「中國，我們和你在一起」的標語牌，表達對中國抗擊疫情的關注和支持。日本、俄羅斯、美國、梵蒂岡等國早前也通過向中國寄送醫療物資支援抗疫。<br />\n（新華社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/article/20200221/s00013/1582223878808/%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%89%93%E6%B0%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2Farticle%2F20200221%2Fs00013%2F1582223878808%2F%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%25B0%25A3&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqF0cTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=4363eedf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2Farticle%2F20200221%2Fs00013%2F1582223878808%2F%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%25B0%25A3&h=3b0559e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/article/20200221/s00013/1582223878808/%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%89%93%E6%B0%A3</a>"},{"pid":"e5fde083569e57cd65a29afe8ebd3068e4f5a913","tid":1889980,"uid":92908,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-0